components.name: Load & Modify Facilities Data
components.description: Ingests facilities.csv, cleans and standardizes address formats, and converts the data to JSON using the loadandmodify service.

upstream_policy.description: Runs independently as the first step.

connections.purpose: Shared data directory mounted into containers

components.name: Geocode Facilities (HERE)
components.description: Geocodes facility locations using the address field via the HERE API, adding latitude and longitude to each record.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful loading and modification of facilities data.

connections.purpose: Shared data directory mounted into containers

components.name: Calculate Distance to Public Transport
components.description: Calculates the distance from each facility to the nearest public transportation stop/hub and adds a distance_to_pt column.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful geocoding of facilities.

connections.purpose: Shared data directory mounted into containers

components.name: Calculate Distance to Residential Areas
components.description: Calculates the distance from each facility to the nearest residential area center/boundary and adds a distance_to_residential column.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after distance to public transport has been calculated.

connections.purpose: Shared data directory mounted into containers

components.name: Save Final Facility Accessibility Data
components.description: Exports the enriched facility accessibility data to a CSV file.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after all distance calculations have completed.

connections.purpose: Shared data directory mounted into containers
